CREATE PROC [dbo].[ImportFactStreaming] AS begin

insert into dbo.FactStreaming
(
	TransactionID
	, CustomerSK
	, MovieSK
	, StreamStartDateSK
	, StreamStartTimeSK
	, StreamEndDateSK
	, StreamEndTimeSK
	, StreamDurationSec
	, StreamDurationMin
)
select
	s.SourceSystemTransactionID
	, c.CustomerSK
	, m.MovieSK
	, ssd.DateSK
	, sst.TimeSK
	, sed.DateSK
	, [set].TimeSK
	, datediff(second, s.StreamStart, s.StreamEnd) as StreamDurationSec
	, datediff(second, s.StreamStart, s.StreamEnd) / 60.0 as StreamDurationMin
from extern.streaming s
inner join dbo.DimCustomers c on c.CustomerID = s.CustomerID
inner join dbo.DimMovies m on m.MovieID = s.MovieID
inner join dbo.DimDate as ssd on ssd.DateValue = cast(s.StreamStart as date)
inner join dbo.DimTime as sst on sst.TimeValue = cast(s.StreamStart as time(0))
left outer join dbo.DimDate as sed on sed.DateValue = cast(s.StreamEnd as date)
left outer join dbo.DimTime as [set] on [set].TimeValue = cast(s.StreamEnd as time(0))
where
	not exists (select 1 from dbo.FactStreaming f where f.TransactionID = s.SourceSystemTransactionID)

END
GO
